{"tid":2027434,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Sell HK天水圍Wetland Seasons Park超額認購49倍","createTime":"2020-05-21T11:35:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T14:29:56.000Z","uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bbf5396d5fc154ecbc4e923b744798e5a2d1d22a","tid":2027434,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T11:35:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2645000/2649442/W01_1024.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2645000%2F2649442%2FW01_1024.jpeg&h=72022e4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新盤大混戰，天水圍Wetland Seasons Park第2期周六開賣200伙，今截收購樓意向登記。新地回應指，核數仍在進行中，初步點算約1萬個登記。以此計算，初步超額認購49倍。<br />\n<br />\n周六銷售將分成2組，別墅單位及3房戶將首先揀樓，大手買家可優先，其後為2房戶或以下單位。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，第1期1月初開售時，首輪截收7,370個認購登記，而今次第2期反應勝過第1期之餘，更成為今年最多認購登記的全新盤。<br />\n<br />\n記者：梁子謙<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2649442/Wetland%20Seasons%20Park%E7%AC%AC2%E6%9C%9F%E6%94%B6%E7%B4%841%E8%90%AC%E5%80%8B%E8%AA%8D%E8%B3%BC%E7%99%BB%E8%A8%98%20%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%9A?mtc=60007\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2649442%2FWetland%2520Seasons%2520Park%25E7%25AC%25AC2%25E6%259C%259F%25E6%2594%25B6%25E7%25B4%25841%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2580%258B%25E8%25AA%258D%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E7%2599%25BB%25E8%25A8%2598%2520%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A4%259A%3Fmtc%3D60007&d=%2FbZU6AtRr1oB2SY8YhhoVz2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=4009b40a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2649442/Wetland%20Seasons%20Park%E7%AC%AC2%E6%9C%9F%E6%94%B6%E7%B4%841%E8%90%AC%E5%80%8B%E8%AA%8D%E8%B3%BC%E7%99%BB%E8%A8%98%20%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%9A?mtc=60007</a>"},{"pid":"92a092f384dda58550fdf3a0f80f852cbda9ad9e","tid":2027434,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T11:38:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na